{"tid":1482252,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"著黑衫著黑衫著黑衫","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:52:04.000Z","uid":94809,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5cab3945a38fe0a223b9a516e0f8efe92c30bd83","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"從來著黑衫唔係代表勇武，黑衫係代表對政權既恐懼，係大家既保護色。如果大家覺得黑衫係比人標籤，其實已經係一種<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白色恐怖</span>，大家要記住，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地從來都唔係暴力人士</span>，勇武係一種心態，唔係透過衣著反映，大家可以諗番<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中大學生full gear同校長</strong></span>既對話，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑衫係對政權既恐懼阿！</span>大家一齊著黑衫，姐係大家都企喺手足果邊，係一種支持，一種打氣！<br />\n<br />\n但如果你依然覺得彩虹係等終多元化，去做，我只係想表達黑衫既意思！兄弟爬山，希望大家可以諗下我講既野。<br />\n<br />\n臨時臨急打呢篇野係因為一起身就聽到朋友話今日彩虹戰衣。唔好意思，我打到一舊舊，希望大家諗諗佢，就後要出門口啦！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7f88ee10d4bfa1ae875760025b7ffeefcc6ac59e","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"推到有人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230de9298b398366ba85b39fce2dc3e109fd01c6","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"推到有人見到"},{"pid":"67b48c0a605d96aae0bcba12a0092aa84be384fb","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"推到有人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46710ee67d4c5117acdf949694ca98b2a59de6e","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"快啲睇！"},{"pid":"a45ac8caae140917716049aa1d4a6455c5e7f416","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e008d65c49654c4ac9e8249f46b2bb5c9178ce81","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"推阿！"},{"pid":"8c5c0d6c26945660b636eeaed0f197217e3725c0","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8916dcd1d55deb647d7832a4aff58bb097d20489","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"26cb1bb7503ebd5ac936b042a100fe1a1b74219a","tid":1482252,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}